Our Goals.




Seek the consumer and customer insights that yield compelling new brand promises, product propositions,
				and service strategies.
				
Know your product's chooser, user, and influencer with a clear understanding of their functional and emotional
				need states.
				
Create a complete product or service experience focused on maximizing the impact of your strategic program, 
				technology, and/or design choices.
				
To delight all those who interact with your brand at all its various touchpoints.




About Us.




Denise Archambault, Ph.D., is the Owner/President of The Consumer Compass, Inc. Denise has spent over 20 years
				in the fields of Consumer Psychology, Consumer Insights, and Market Research.
				
Jenny Bouman is the Research Manager for The Consumer Compass, Inc. Jenny has also worked in the field of Market
				Research for over 20 years.

