Who We Are












Compass Display and Promotion, a family-owned business founded by Joseph Carugati in 1969, provides a wide variety of product sampling and other merchandising services for the building and flooring industries. Compass is headquartered in Trenton NJ, with multiple locations for extensive production and warehousing capabilities.
Compass Retail Display Group supports the growing demand for retail displays and fixtures. Headquartered in Northeast Philadelphia, we manufacture high-quality point-of-purchase displays and retail fixtures through their extensive collection of state-of-the-art equipment.
The combination of these facilities and capabilities allows us to provide our customers with a comprehensive offering of merchandising products and services.
WE ARE COMPASS













© 2017 Compass Display and Promotion Co., Inc. All rights reserved.











 












